WEBVTT

00:00.465 --> 00:01.726
Good Night Moon.

00:02.264 --> 00:03.716
By Margaret Wise Brown.

00:04.309 --> 00:05.925
Pictures by Clement Hurd.

00:18.595 --> 00:23.869
In the great green room, there was a telephone, and a red balloon,...

00:26.119 --> 00:30.174
...and a picture of the cow jumping over the moon.

00:32.356 --> 00:34.798
And there were three little bears sitting on chairs,...

00:36.579 --> 00:37.604
...and two little kittens,...

00:38.713 --> 00:39.945
...and a pair of mittens.

00:41.335 --> 00:42.661
And a little toy house,...

00:44.293 --> 00:45.448
...and a young mouse.

00:47.192 --> 00:50.710
And a comb, and a brush, and a bowl full of mush.

00:53.990 --> 00:57.913
And a quiet old lady who was whispering "hush".

01:04.707 --> 01:05.732
Good night room.

01:10.931 --> 01:12.148
Good night moon.

01:13.744 --> 01:16.195
Good night cow jumping over the moon.

01:18.502 --> 01:21.245
Good night light, and the red balloon.

01:22.665 --> 01:23.812
Good night bears.

01:25.106 --> 01:26.633
Good night chairs.

01:30.195 --> 01:31.213
Good night kittens.

01:32.140 --> 01:33.864
And good night mittens.

01:35.717 --> 01:36.927
Good night clocks.

01:38.200 --> 01:39.685
And good night socks.

01:41.067 --> 01:44.984
Good night little house and good night mouse.

01:50.238 --> 01:52.333
Good night comb and good night brush.

01:53.503 --> 01:54.646
Good night nobody.

01:55.819 --> 01:56.907
Good night mush.

02:00.043 --> 02:05.067
And good night to the old lady whispering "hush".

02:07.814 --> 02:08.957
Good night stars.

02:10.415 --> 02:11.788
Good night air.

02:19.045 --> 02:23.170
Good night noises, everywhere.

